{\*\bkmkstart co_g_ID0EWGAE_1}{\*\bkmkend co_g_ID0EWGAE_1}What made the fellow-servant rule so attractive to the judges in the generation }{\hich\af5\loch\cf19\strike0\fs20\i\ulnone\ulc0\b0\f5\loch
after Farwell?}{\hich\af5\loch\cf19\strike0\fs20\i0\ulnone\ulc0\b0\f5\loch
 There were probably a number of reasons; and scholars do not agree on this point.}{{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "#co_footnote_F9539209744_1" }{\fldrslt {\hich\af5\loch\hich\af5\loch\cf19\strike0\super\f5\fs16\i0\ulnone\ulc0\b0\cf19\strike0\super\fs16\i0\ulnone\ulc0\b0\f5\loch
{\*\bkmkstart co_fnRef_F9539209744_ID0EDHAE_1}{\*\bkmkend co_fnRef_F9539209744_ID0EDHAE_1}9}{}}}\hich\af5\loch\cf19\strike0\fs20\i0\ulnone\ulc0\b0\f5\loch
 Shaw\u8217\'92s opinion gives, I believe, some clues. In one passage in the opinion, Shaw, referring to Farwell\u8217\'92s injury, calls it a \u8220\'93loss [that] must be deemed to be the result of a pure accident, like those to which all men, in all employments, and at all times, are more or less exposed\u8221\'94}{{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "#co_footnote_F10539209744_1" }{\fldrslt {\hich\af5\loch\hich\af5\loch\cf19\strike0\super\f5\fs16\i0\ulnone\ulc0\b0\cf19\strike0\super\fs16\i0\ulnone\ulc0\b0\f5\loch
