 Like \u8220\'93similar losses from accidental causes, it must rest where it first fell.\u8221\'94}{{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "#co_footnote_F11539209744_1" }{\fldrslt {\hich\af5\loch\hich\af5\loch\cf19\strike0\super\f5\fs16\i0\ulnone\ulc0\b0\cf19\strike0\super\fs16\i0\ulnone\ulc0\b0\f5\loch
