By the end of the century, even though the fellow servant rule was still a major obstacle, tort cases, some of them arising out of industrial accidents, were common in the courts.}{{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "#co_footnote_F24539209744_1" }{\fldrslt {\hich\af5\loch\hich\af5\loch\cf19\strike0\super\f5\fs16\i0\ulnone\ulc0\b0\cf19\strike0\super\fs16\i0\ulnone\ulc0\b0\f5\loch
