 and laws of this sort were common by the early twentieth century: laws applying to railroad accidents, or accidents in mines, and (in a few instances) applying more broadly.}{{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "#co_footnote_F28539209744_1" }{\fldrslt {\hich\af5\loch\hich\af5\loch\cf19\strike0\super\f5\fs16\i0\ulnone\ulc0\b0\cf19\strike0\super\fs16\i0\ulnone\ulc0\b0\f5\loch
