{\*\bkmkstart co_g_ID0EEWAE_1}{\*\bkmkend co_g_ID0EEWAE_1}In the states, a somewhat more radical path was followed: the enactment of workers\u8217\'92 compensation law, a system which essentially guaranteed recovery for industrial accidents.}{{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "#co_footnote_F36539209744_1" }{\fldrslt {\hich\af5\loch\hich\af5\loch\cf19\strike0\super\f5\fs16\i0\ulnone\ulc0\b0\cf19\strike0\super\fs16\i0\ulnone\ulc0\b0\f5\loch
{\*\bkmkstart co_fnRef_F36539209744_ID0EMWAE_1}{\*\bkmkend co_fnRef_F36539209744_ID0EMWAE_1}36}{}}}\hich\af5\loch\cf19\strike0\fs20\i0\ulnone\ulc0\b0\f5\loch
 The general idea had been discussed for years. A British compensation law had become law in 1897; a German plan had been adopted even earlier.}{{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "#co_footnote_F37539209744_1" }{\fldrslt {\hich\af5\loch\hich\af5\loch\cf19\strike0\super\f5\fs16\i0\ulnone\ulc0\b0\cf19\strike0\super\fs16\i0\ulnone\ulc0\b0\f5\loch
{\*\bkmkstart co_fnRef_F37539209744_ID0EUWAE_1}{\*\bkmkend co_fnRef_F37539209744_ID0EUWAE_1}37}{}}}\hich\af5\loch\cf19\strike0\fs20\i0\ulnone\ulc0\b0\f5\loch
 Many European countries worked out plans along more or less similar lines. The idea, in short, was more or less in the air. Crystal Eastman\u8217\'92s Pittsburgh study came out strongly in favor of \u8220\'93a law requiring employers to compensate all employees injured according to a uniform method;\u8221\'94}{{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "#co_footnote_F38539209744_1" }{\fldrslt {\hich\af5\loch\hich\af5\loch\cf19\strike0\super\f5\fs16\i0\ulnone\ulc0\b0\cf19\strike0\super\fs16\i0\ulnone\ulc0\b0\f5\loch
{\*\bkmkstart co_fnRef_F38539209744_ID0ELXAE_1}{\*\bkmkend co_fnRef_F38539209744_ID0ELXAE_1}38}{}}}\hich\af5\loch\cf19\strike0\fs20\i0\ulnone\ulc0\b0\f5\loch
 a law of this type, covering industrial accidents, would do away with the slow, inadequate, unjust and \u8220\'93wasteful\u8221\'94 system of tort law}{{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "#co_footnote_F39539209744_1" }{\fldrslt {\hich\af5\loch\hich\af5\loch\cf19\strike0\super\f5\fs16\i0\ulnone\ulc0\b0\cf19\strike0\super\fs16\i0\ulnone\ulc0\b0\f5\loch
{\*\bkmkstart co_fnRef_F39539209744_ID0EOXAE_1}{\*\bkmkend co_fnRef_F39539209744_ID0EOXAE_1}39}}}}
