{\*\bkmkstart co_g_ID0EOGAG_1}{\*\bkmkend co_g_ID0EOGAG_1}The compensation laws had grown out of the dark world described by Crystal Eastman: a grim and perilous world, the world of coal mines, construction sites, railroad yards, and factories full of whirling, dangerous machines.}{{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "#co_footnote_F69539209744_1" }{\fldrslt {\hich\af5\loch\hich\af5\loch\cf19\strike0\super\f5\fs16\i0\ulnone\ulc0\b0\cf19\strike0\super\fs16\i0\ulnone\ulc0\b0\f5\loch
