 This was hardly the usual sort of industrial accident. Was it compensable? The court said yes. Stark\u8217\'92s death was the result of \u8220\'93a hazard incident to employment as a street-car conductor\u8221\'94}{{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "#co_footnote_F71539209744_1" }{\fldrslt {\hich\af5\loch\hich\af5\loch\cf19\strike0\super\f5\fs16\i0\ulnone\ulc0\b0\cf19\strike0\super\fs16\i0\ulnone\ulc0\b0\f5\loch
