{\*\bkmkstart co_g_ID0EZ4AG_1}{\*\bkmkend co_g_ID0EZ4AG_1}This gap in the welfare system has made its mark on the tort system as a whole. That system, as John Witt has pointed out, is a \u8220\'93patchwork;\u8221\'94 a \u8220\'93hodge podge of systems,\u8221\'94 an \u8220\'93accidental product\u8221\'94}{{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "#co_footnote_F118539209744_1" }{\fldrslt {\hich\af5\loch\hich\af5\loch\cf19\strike0\super\f5\fs16\i0\ulnone\ulc0\b0\cf19\strike0\super\fs16\i0\ulnone\ulc0\b0\f5\loch
